data.title: Kris Aquino and James Yap Turn Valentine
data.meta_description:
Kris Aquino and James Yap Turn Valentine - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. 1) Kris Aquino and James Yap celebrated their birthdays together on Valentine's Day at a restaurant in Makati City. 
2) Many celebrities attended the party, including James Yap's basketball teammates, politicians, and actors.
3) Both Kris and James expressed wishes for good health and a smooth relationship going forward amid past challenges.
